casebody.data:
Dayton Bar Association v. Gross.

[Cite as Dayton Bar Asm v. Gross (1995), 73 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 91-1251 Submitted June 21, 1995 Decided June 22, 1995.)

*1202For earlier case, see Dayton Bar Assn. v. Gross (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 224, 581 N.E.2d 520.

Moyer, C.J., Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Douglas and Cook, JJ., would require petitioner to submit an agreement with his sister as a condition of his reinstatement.
